UPDATE game SET description = 'Sea of Thieves is a shared-world pirate adventure built around sailing, teamwork, treasure hunting, and the unpredictable chaos of the open sea. The game shines most when played with friends, because managing a ship, scanning the horizon, and surviving sudden disasters all feel better as a group effort. Its ocean is beautiful and dynamic, with storms, waves, and changing light giving every voyage a strong sense of atmosphere. Encounters with other crews create some of the game''s best stories, whether through combat, alliances, betrayal, or simple panic. Quests provide structure, but much of the magic comes from unexpected moments that emerge naturally during travel. The stylized presentation keeps the world playful even when the danger rises. It is a multiplayer sandbox that succeeds because it constantly turns simple goals into memorable adventures.' WHERE title = 'Sea of Thieves';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Mass Effect Legendary Edition brings together one of gaming''s most beloved science-fiction trilogies in a polished and accessible package. Across all three games, players guide Commander Shepard through a galaxy threatened by extinction, shaping relationships, alliances, and major outcomes along the way. What makes the series special is how choices and bonds carry emotional weight across an enormous arc. Combat and exploration evolve from one entry to the next, but the heart of the trilogy remains its characters and worldbuilding. Alien cultures, political tensions, and squadmate loyalty missions give the universe real texture and identity. The remaster helps modernize the experience while preserving the strengths that made the series iconic. It remains one of the most important examples of large-scale narrative RPG storytelling.' WHERE title = 'Mass Effect Legendary Edition';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Days Gone is an open-world survival adventure set in a post-pandemic America overrun by infected creatures and fractured human factions. Players control Deacon St. John, a drifter whose journey mixes personal grief, motorcycle travel, and desperate survival. The bike is central to the experience, acting not only as transportation but as a tool that must be repaired, upgraded, and protected. The Pacific Northwest setting gives the world a rugged identity, with forests, roads, camps, and abandoned towns creating a convincing sense of distance. Large hordes of infected are one of the game''s standout features, turning encounters into frantic battles of planning, traps, and endurance. While the story takes time to unfold, it grows stronger as its characters and relationships deepen. The result is a rough but emotionally sincere open-world journey with strong atmosphere.' WHERE title = 'Days Gone';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Detroit: Become Human is a branching narrative adventure that explores android consciousness, morality, and social unrest in a near-future city. Players follow multiple protagonists whose stories intersect through choice-driven scenes that can lead to very different outcomes. The game''s structure makes every decision feel immediate, whether it involves compassion, rebellion, sacrifice, or fear. Its presentation is highly cinematic, using performance capture and visual detail to emphasize emotion and tension. What gives the experience its power is the way it invites players to question control, freedom, and identity from multiple viewpoints. Replaying scenes can reveal just how many paths were possible all along. It is a polished interactive drama built around consequence, empathy, and speculation about what it means to be alive.' WHERE title = 'Detroit: Become Human';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Batman: Arkham Knight is a superhero action game that combines stealth, free-flow combat, and open-world exploration in a dark version of Gotham City. Players once again become Batman, gliding across rooftops, hunting criminals, and facing a city pushed toward collapse by fear and chaos. Combat remains fluid and satisfying, allowing players to chain strikes, counters, gadgets, and takedowns with confidence. Predator encounters continue to be a defining strength, turning enclosed spaces into tactical stealth playgrounds. Gotham itself is detailed and atmospheric, full of rain, neon, and decay that suits the character perfectly. The Batmobile adds scale and spectacle, even if it changes the rhythm of the series in noticeable ways. It is a stylish, feature-rich conclusion to the Arkham trilogy.' WHERE title = 'Batman: Arkham Knight';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Remnant II is a cooperative action shooter that blends firearm combat, melee options, class systems, and difficult boss fights into a flexible RPG structure. Players travel through shifting worlds full of strange enemies, secrets, and alternate layouts that make repeated playthroughs feel rewarding. Combat is challenging without becoming rigid, encouraging adaptation through archetypes, weapon mods, and teamwork. The procedural elements help each campaign feel slightly different, giving exploration a stronger sense of uncertainty. Boss encounters often demand observation and quick reactions, especially when playing solo. Co-op significantly enhances the experience, turning intense battles into shared problem-solving. It is a strong follow-up that builds on the original''s unusual mix of shooter action and fantasy danger.' WHERE title = 'Remnant II';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Star Wars Jedi: Survivor continues Cal Kestis''s story with a larger world, stronger traversal, and a more confident sense of cinematic adventure. The game expands on the combat foundations of Fallen Order by adding more stances, more movement options, and more expressive encounter design. Lightsaber battles feel energetic and responsive, especially as players learn how different forms suit different threats. Exploration is broader this time, with hub-like areas, hidden routes, and optional activities that give the world more room to breathe. The tone balances personal struggle, resistance, and the weight of survival in an era dominated by the Empire. Its best moments come when spectacle and emotional character beats work together naturally. It is a bigger and more polished continuation of Cal''s journey.' WHERE title = 'Star Wars Jedi: Survivor™';

UPDATE game SET description = 'STAR WARS Jedi: Fallen Order is a story-driven action adventure that follows Cal Kestis as he tries to survive the aftermath of Order 66 and reconnect with the Force. The game combines lightsaber combat, platforming, environmental puzzles, and metroidvania-style exploration into a cohesive structure. Combat rewards timing, parries, and patience rather than pure aggression, giving duels a satisfying rhythm. The planets are designed with enough verticality and locked-off areas to encourage return visits as new abilities are unlocked. Its strongest appeal comes from delivering a focused single-player Star Wars experience during a time when many players were hungry for exactly that. The story gives Cal and his companions enough room to become emotionally grounded rather than just functional. It is a solid and memorable Jedi adventure with strong atmosphere and momentum.' WHERE title = 'STAR WARS Jedi: Fallen Order™';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Dying Light 2 Stay Human is an open-world survival action game built around first-person parkour, urban traversal, and dangerous encounters with the infected. Movement is central to the experience, and the ability to leap across rooftops, climb buildings, and escape danger quickly gives the game a unique sense of speed. Day and night create very different moods, with nighttime bringing greater rewards but far more terrifying risks. Combat mixes improvised weapons, environmental hazards, and close-range desperation in a way that suits the ruined city setting. Player decisions also shape factions and districts, giving parts of the world a reactive feel. The strongest moments often come from rooftop travel and panic-filled escapes rather than direct fighting. It is an energetic survival adventure defined by motion and pressure.' WHERE title = 'Dying Light 2 Stay Human: Reloaded Edition';

UPDATE game SET description = 'The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim Special Edition is a legendary open-world fantasy RPG that continues to attract players because of its scale, freedom, and atmosphere. As the Dragonborn, players can wander through mountains, crypts, cities, and wilds while shaping a personal path through quests, guilds, and character builds. The game''s greatest strength is how naturally it supports both grand adventures and quiet roleplay. Magic, stealth, melee, crafting, and exploration all combine to make progression feel personal rather than prescribed. Its northern setting is filled with mythic tension, from dragon attacks and civil war to ancient ruins and forgotten prophecies. Even after many years, the world remains easy to get lost in for hours at a time. It is one of the most enduring fantasy sandboxes ever created.' WHERE title = 'The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim Special Edition';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Fallout 4 is an open-world RPG set in a devastated future where ruins, radiation, and strange communities define everyday survival. Players emerge from vault life into the Commonwealth, searching for answers while also deciding what kind of person they want to become in a fractured society. Gunplay is more immediate than in earlier entries, giving exploration and combat a smoother rhythm. Base building adds a management layer that encourages players to invest in the world physically rather than just move through it. The retro-futuristic tone remains one of the game''s strongest qualities, mixing dark humor with bleak collapse. Factions, companions, and environmental storytelling help make the wasteland feel full of histories and tensions. It is a broad and highly moddable sandbox RPG with a distinct identity.' WHERE title = 'Fallout 4';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Red Dead Redemption is a western action adventure centered on John Marston, a former outlaw forced back into violence by the government. The game''s world captures the dying frontier with dusty towns, dangerous roads, and a sense of historical transition that gives the journey unusual melancholy. Its story is tightly focused, using revenge, duty, and personal cost to drive the player forward. Gunfights, horseback travel, and side activities support the fantasy of living in a fading western landscape. The writing balances humor, tragedy, and social commentary in a way that still holds up strongly. John Marston remains one of Rockstar''s most compelling protagonists because of the quiet sadness beneath his toughness. It is a defining western game and an important foundation for the series'' later evolution.' WHERE title = 'Red Dead Redemption';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Assassins Creed Mirage is a more focused entry in the long-running series, emphasizing stealth, urban traversal, and targeted assassinations over sprawling RPG progression. Set in Baghdad, the game leans into dense streets, rooftops, and social stealth in ways that recall earlier Assassin''s Creed titles. Basim''s story gives the narrative a more personal and introspective tone than some of the larger recent entries. Assassination tools, movement routes, and compact mission design encourage careful planning instead of brute-force combat. The city itself is full of detail and atmosphere, helping the return to a more classical structure feel intentional rather than small. It is less about overwhelming scale and more about precision and identity. For many players, that focus is exactly what makes it refreshing.' WHERE title = 'Assassins Creed Mirage';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Assassins Creed Valhalla is a huge action RPG that follows Eivor through conquest, alliance-building, and settlement life in Dark Ages England. The game combines raiding, exploration, mythic storylines, and political maneuvering inside an enormous open world. Combat is heavier and more direct than in earlier entries, fitting the Viking theme through axes, shields, and brutal impact. The settlement system gives the player a home base that slowly evolves with progress, reinforcing long-term attachment to the journey. Regional arcs make the structure feel episodic, with each territory acting like a chapter in a wider saga. Mythological elements add a larger spiritual dimension to the story without replacing its historical core. It is a vast, content-rich adventure for players who enjoy immersion through scale and accumulation.' WHERE title = 'Assassins Creed Valhalla';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Far Cry 6 is an open-world shooter set in Yara, a tropical dictatorship struggling under oppression and rebellion. Players fight as Dani Rojas, joining a guerrilla movement to challenge a brutal regime across cities, coasts, forests, and military strongholds. The game leans into improvisation, allowing players to combine weapons, gadgets, animal companions, and explosive tools in creative ways. Open-world design emphasizes player freedom, with outposts, side missions, treasure hunts, and combat spaces supporting many different approaches. Its presentation is colorful and chaotic, mixing serious political framing with playful weapon concepts and large-scale destruction. The setting helps the game stand out visually, especially when travel and conflict reveal Yara''s beauty and violence side by side. It is a confident, energetic sandbox shooter that knows exactly what kind of fun it wants to deliver.' WHERE title = 'Far Cry 6';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Borderlands 3 is a looter shooter built around over-the-top weapons, fast co-op action, and constant reward loops. The gun variety is one of its biggest strengths, making loot drops feel exciting because weapons often behave in absurd and distinctive ways. Character classes offer enough identity to support multiple playstyles, whether players prefer mobility, pets, raw damage, or support abilities. The campaign bounces between planets and factions, keeping the visual palette broad even when the humor stays consistently loud. Co-op play enhances nearly everything, turning chaotic battles into shared spectacles of explosions and improvisation. Its endgame systems and post-launch support also help extend replay value for dedicated players. It is a colorful and highly kinetic shooter that thrives on excess.' WHERE title = 'Borderlands 3';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Titanfall 2 is a science-fiction shooter celebrated for its remarkable movement, excellent campaign design, and unforgettable mech combat. Players shift between agile on-foot parkour and the heavy power of Titans, creating a rhythm unlike almost any other FPS. The campaign is especially loved because it introduces new ideas constantly, making every level feel purposeful and surprising. Gunplay is smooth and expressive, but the movement system is what gives the game its signature energy. The bond between pilot and Titan also gives the story more emotional resonance than many expected from the genre. Multiplayer extends the same speed and creativity into competitive matches that reward momentum and precision. It remains one of the most admired shooters of its era.' WHERE title = 'Titanfall® 2';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Battlefield 1 is a large-scale military shooter that uses the First World War as the foundation for dramatic, atmospheric, and often chaotic multiplayer battles. The game is especially effective at presentation, using sound, weather, destruction, and visual detail to create a sense of scale and intensity. Classes, vehicles, and shifting frontline objectives help matches feel dynamic rather than static. Its campaign vignettes also give brief but memorable perspectives on different fronts of the war. Weapons and movement are tuned to create tension without sacrificing playability or spectacle. More than many shooters, it succeeds at making conflict feel overwhelming and cinematic. It stands out as one of the strongest modern Battlefield entries.' WHERE title = 'Battlefield™ 1';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Battlefield V is a team-based military shooter that returns to World War II with squad mechanics, environmental destruction, and strong moment-to-moment combat. The game focuses on positioning, support roles, and coordinated movement in ways that reward teamwork. Gunplay is crisp and satisfying, especially in medium-range encounters where player awareness matters as much as reflex. Vehicles and combined-arms battles remain central to the identity of the series, adding scale and unpredictability to many matches. While it had a complicated post-launch reputation, the core combat systems are often praised for their immediacy and polish. Maps and modes allow for both more tactical pacing and full chaotic warfare. It is a capable large-scale shooter with strong mechanical foundations.' WHERE title = 'Battlefield™ V';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Valheim is a survival sandbox inspired by Norse mythology, built around exploration, building, resource gathering, and steady progression through dangerous biomes. The game''s world feels open and inviting, but also quietly threatening, especially when storms roll in or the wilderness turns hostile at night. Building systems are flexible enough to support both practical outposts and elaborate halls, which is a huge part of the game''s appeal. Combat is straightforward but meaningful, especially as tougher enemies force better preparation. Co-op play turns the experience into a satisfying cycle of expedition, crafting, and shared achievement. The visual style is simple, yet the lighting and environmental mood often make it unexpectedly beautiful. It is one of the most absorbing survival games for players who enjoy long-form progression and communal play.' WHERE title = 'Valheim';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Palworld is an open-world survival game that mixes creature collecting, crafting, shooting, and base management in a way that feels deliberately strange and highly watchable. Players capture companion creatures and then use them for combat, work, exploration, and production in a world full of systems to optimize. That contrast between cute design and hard survival utility is a big part of the game''s unusual identity. Exploration is broad and often rewarding, with different environments, enemy camps, and material demands pushing players outward. Base growth becomes increasingly important as the game progresses, especially when automation begins to take shape. Cooperative play adds more chaos and creativity to the entire loop. It succeeds because it embraces weirdness while still being a functional survival sandbox.' WHERE title = 'Palworld';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Subnautica is an underwater survival game that combines fear, curiosity, and beauty in one of the genre''s most memorable worlds. Players crash-land on an alien ocean planet and must gradually learn its ecosystems, resources, and hidden dangers in order to survive and escape. The sense of discovery is extraordinary, especially because deeper regions become more mysterious and intimidating instead of simply harder. Crafting and base-building support exploration rather than replace it, giving players practical reasons to push further into the unknown. Audio design and environmental scale make the ocean feel both peaceful and terrifying depending on where you are. The story unfolds quietly through ruins, logs, and gradual realization rather than constant exposition. It is one of the best examples of survival design driven by wonder.' WHERE title = 'Subnautica';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Outer Wilds is a time-loop exploration game built around curiosity, knowledge, and the joy of slowly understanding a solar system. Players pilot a small ship between planets that are all changing in real time, each one shaped by unique rules and mysteries. There is no traditional leveling or combat progression because the true advancement comes from what the player learns. That design makes every discovery feel deeply personal and meaningful. The writing is gentle and philosophical, touching on mortality, legacy, and cosmic scale without becoming heavy-handed. Its soundtrack and atmosphere give the entire journey a reflective tone that lingers long after completion. It is a rare game where knowledge itself becomes the most powerful mechanic.' WHERE title = 'Outer Wilds';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Slay the Spire is a deckbuilding roguelike that turns card synergy, resource management, and route planning into an endlessly replayable strategy loop. Each run asks players to build around relics, card upgrades, and encounters that may or may not support a larger plan. The brilliance of the design lies in how simple the rules feel compared to the depth they produce over time. Every new card reward becomes a small strategic test of discipline and long-term thinking. Different characters encourage completely different styles, which helps keep repeated runs fresh. Randomness exists, but strong decision-making still feels highly rewarded. It is one of the most influential and refined strategy indies of the past decade.' WHERE title = 'Slay the Spire';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Cuphead is a run-and-gun action game famous for its hand-drawn 1930s cartoon art, jazz-influenced soundtrack, and punishing boss encounters. The visual style is instantly recognizable, but the gameplay is equally important because it demands precision, pattern recognition, and calm under pressure. Boss phases are inventive and often wildly theatrical, turning every fight into a performance as much as a challenge. Movement and shooting are simple on paper, yet the game extracts enormous depth from exact timing and positioning. The difficulty can be intense, but the short retry loop keeps players focused and learning. Cooperative play adds a second layer of excitement and chaos. It is a beautiful and demanding action game with a very strong identity.' WHERE title = 'Cuphead';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Forza Motorsport is a racing simulation focused on performance driving, track mastery, and the feel of competitive precision. The game emphasizes braking points, cornering discipline, and gradual improvement rather than the festival-style freedom of Horizon. Cars feel distinct enough to reward tuning and experimentation, especially for players who enjoy dialing in setups. Track presentation is clean and polished, supporting the more serious motorsport atmosphere. Progression encourages continued learning rather than casual collection alone. Multiplayer and event structure help give races a stronger sense of stakes and craft. It is built for players who enjoy racing as skill development rather than pure spectacle.' WHERE title = 'Forza Motorsport';

UPDATE game SET description = 'EA SPORTS FC 24 is a modern football simulation built around licensed clubs, recognizable stars, and competitive online play. The game aims to capture the pace and shape of contemporary football through movement, passing, defensive control, and tactical variation. Career-style modes and team-building systems give players different reasons to engage depending on whether they prefer solo progression or live competition. Presentation is highly polished, reinforcing the feeling of a global sport product with big-match energy. Its core appeal lies in recreating familiar clubs and players in a system that rewards timing and understanding of space. Frequent play is encouraged through events, progression, and the social dimension of football culture itself. It is a strong continuation of the big-budget football sim formula.' WHERE title = 'EA SPORTS FC™ 24';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Mortal Kombat 1 is a cinematic fighting game that combines brutal finishing moves, stylish character design, and accessible but satisfying combat systems. The rebooted timeline gives the story mode room to revisit familiar rivalries with a fresh structure. Fighting feels punchy and dramatic, with strong visual clarity and a reliable sense of impact. Assist mechanics expand combo routes and strategy, helping the game feel modern without losing the recognizable Mortal Kombat identity. Presentation is lavish, especially during story scenes and signature finishing sequences. Longtime fans benefit from the roster''s legacy, while newer players can still enjoy the clear spectacle of each match. It is a polished and highly entertaining entry in one of fighting games'' most recognizable franchises.' WHERE title = 'Mortal Kombat 1';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Sifu is a martial arts action game built around close-range precision, relentless pressure, and the gradual mastery of timing. The central aging mechanic turns repeated failure into a thematic and mechanical system, forcing players to think about progress, cost, and momentum. Combat is all about reading attacks, managing space, and staying calm in crowded encounters. Animations and environmental interactions make fights feel grounded and choreographed at the same time. Levels are compact but replayable, encouraging players to revisit them with greater skill and efficiency. Its tone is serious and disciplined, which helps the action feel focused rather than flashy for its own sake. It is one of the most satisfying recent games about learning through repetition.' WHERE title = 'Sifu';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Returnal is a third-person sci-fi action game that combines roguelike structure with fast movement, bullet-hell intensity, and psychological unease. Players control Selene, trapped in a cycle of death on a hostile alien planet where memory and reality keep slipping into one another. Combat is aggressive and mobile, rewarding players who stay in motion instead of hiding from danger. The game''s visual and audio design create a tense atmosphere that supports both action and mystery. The roguelike loop can be demanding, but it also reinforces the story''s themes of repetition and instability. Environmental storytelling and shifting fragments of narrative keep the experience unsettling and compelling. It is a bold, stylish action game with strong identity and pressure.' WHERE title = 'Returnal™';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Ratchet & Clank: Rift Apart is a colorful action adventure that uses dimensional travel, inventive weapons, and animation-quality presentation to deliver constant energy. The game''s arsenal is one of its biggest strengths, with weapons that are imaginative, humorous, and mechanically expressive. Platforming, combat, and world-hopping are woven together so smoothly that the pacing rarely slows down. The visual fidelity is especially striking, making characters, effects, and environments feel bright and alive. Beneath the spectacle, the story also gives room for character reflection and emotional sincerity. It is approachable for newcomers while still clearly rooted in the charm of a long-running series. The result is a highly polished adventure built for fun, momentum, and visual delight.' WHERE title = 'Ratchet & Clank: Rift Apart';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Age of Empires IV: Anniversary Edition is a real-time strategy game that returns the series to large-scale historical conflict with modern production and strong readability. Players gather resources, build armies, and expand civilizations while managing economic growth and battlefield positioning. Each civilization has enough asymmetry to change strategy meaningfully without making the game inaccessible. The documentary-style presentation adds educational texture and helps reinforce the historical framing. Matches can shift from slow economic setup to massive sieges and tactical pressure in ways that feel satisfying and dramatic. Strong multiplayer support and broad single-player content help the game serve different kinds of strategy fans. It is a successful revival that respects the past while feeling contemporary.' WHERE title = 'Age of Empires IV: Anniversary Edition';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Crusader Kings III is a grand strategy role-playing game about dynasties, politics, inheritance, and the chaos of human ambition. Rather than focusing only on military conquest, it asks players to manage families, marriages, religions, schemes, and succession across generations. Characters are central to the experience, and their traits, rivalries, and ambitions often matter more than maps or numbers alone. The game creates memorable emergent stories because systems constantly collide in unexpected ways. Success can come through diplomacy, manipulation, war, or simply surviving disaster long enough to recover. Despite its complexity, the interface and presentation are much more welcoming than many strategy games in its class. It is a brilliant sandbox for players who enjoy storytelling through systems.' WHERE title = 'Crusader Kings III';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Cities: Skylines II is a city-building simulation focused on planning, infrastructure, services, and the slow complexity of urban growth. The game asks players to think about roads, zoning, traffic, education, economy, and environmental systems as one connected whole. Watching a small town expand into a functioning city can be deeply satisfying because every major success usually comes from many smaller design decisions. Its appeal lies less in dramatic events and more in long-form management and optimization. The scale of the simulation supports a strong sense of authorship over the final city. When everything works, the experience feels both creative and analytical. It is designed for players who enjoy watching systems evolve over time under their guidance.' WHERE title = 'Cities: Skylines II';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Project Zomboid is a hardcore zombie survival sandbox built around vulnerability, simulation depth, and the constant possibility of permanent failure. The game does not present survival as a power fantasy, but as a slow and exhausting attempt to endure against overwhelming odds. Every task matters, from barricading windows and cooking food to managing wounds, fatigue, and panic. The isometric view hides surprising depth, with systems that support stealth, crafting, scavenging, farming, and long-term planning. Multiplayer and modding expand the possibilities even further, turning the world into a stage for many different kinds of survival stories. Its tone is bleak, but that bleakness is exactly what makes success feel meaningful. It is one of the most uncompromising and rewarding zombie sandboxes ever made.' WHERE title = 'Project Zomboid';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Alan Wake 2 is a psychological survival horror game that blends detective structure, meta-fiction, and atmospheric terror into a highly stylized narrative experience. The game alternates perspectives and realities in ways that constantly challenge the player''s understanding of what is happening. Combat is sparse enough to remain tense, while investigation and environmental observation play a much larger role in the overall rhythm. The visual design is moody and dense, filled with darkness, reflections, and uncanny imagery that support the game''s themes. Its writing is ambitious, often leaning into layered storytelling rather than simple clarity. This makes the experience stranger, but also more memorable and distinctive. It is a bold horror sequel built around mood, structure, and artistic confidence.' WHERE title = 'Alan Wake 2';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Dead Cells is a roguelite action platformer that thrives on speed, repetition, and the joy of mastering movement and combat together. Every run sends players through branching paths, random gear choices, and escalating threats that test reflexes and decision-making. Combat feels sharp because dodging, attacking, and repositioning all flow naturally into one another. The game rarely wastes time, which helps failure feel motivating instead of frustrating. Unlocks and permanent progression create long-term goals without undermining the challenge of each run. Its visual style is clean and readable, making the intensity easier to process even when things get frantic. It is one of the strongest examples of how elegant action design can support endless replayability.' WHERE title = 'Dead Cells';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Hi-Fi RUSH is a rhythm-based action game that turns combat, movement, and presentation into one unified performance. Even players who are not naturally focused on rhythm can still enjoy the game, but learning to sync attacks to the beat makes everything feel more powerful and expressive. The world is bright, stylized, and packed with playful visual feedback that reinforces the music-driven identity of the game. Combat mixes basic action mechanics with timing bonuses in a way that feels inviting rather than punishing. Character writing and tone keep the story light, energetic, and easy to enjoy. Set pieces and boss fights also lean heavily into timing and spectacle, making the whole experience feel unusually cohesive. It is one of the most joyful and surprising action games in recent years.' WHERE title = 'Hi-Fi RUSH';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Jusant is a climbing adventure focused on movement, pacing, and the emotional pull of ascending a mysterious vertical world. Instead of conventional combat or large-scale action, the game builds tension through route choice, stamina management, and the physical sensation of climbing. The silence and scale of the environments give the journey a meditative tone. Environmental storytelling slowly reveals what happened to the world and why the climb matters. Its mechanics are simple enough to remain approachable, but deliberate enough to keep the player engaged. The game succeeds because it trusts atmosphere and motion to carry the experience. It is quiet, elegant, and refreshingly different from more conventional action titles.' WHERE title = 'Jusant';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Lethal Company is a cooperative horror game where players scavenge abandoned industrial sites for profit while trying to avoid terrifying threats. Communication is everything, because survival often depends on warning teammates, managing routes, and knowing when to run. The game creates fear not just through monsters, but through uncertainty, isolation, and the knowledge that mistakes can spiral quickly. At the same time, its systems also generate absurd comedy, especially when a plan falls apart in seconds. This blend of dread and chaos is what makes it so compelling with friends. The low-key presentation actually helps the horror by leaving room for imagination and panic. It is a multiplayer horror experience driven by tension, teamwork, and unforgettable disasters.' WHERE title = 'Lethal Company';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Terraria is a 2D sandbox adventure built around mining, crafting, fighting, building, and discovering just how much content can exist beneath a deceptively simple surface. The game begins with basic tools and survival, but gradually expands into boss progression, biome exploration, NPC systems, and powerful gear paths. Combat, mobility, and construction all deepen over time, making the sense of growth especially satisfying. Exploration is one of its great strengths, because every new underground layer or distant biome can reveal resources, structures, or threats that reshape goals. Cooperative play enhances the experience further, turning construction and boss fights into shared projects. Its art style is modest, but the density of systems and surprises gives it huge staying power. It remains one of the best sandbox games ever made.' WHERE title = 'Terraria';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Vampire Survivors is a survival action game built around automatic attacks, movement-based decision-making, and the hypnotic satisfaction of exponential power growth. The premise is simple, but the way upgrades, weapons, and evolutions combine creates a highly addictive feedback loop. Early survival is often tense, but later minutes can become gloriously chaotic as the screen fills with enemies and effects. Unlock systems, hidden interactions, and strange secrets add far more depth than the game initially suggests. Its visual style is deliberately plain, which only makes the elegance of the design more impressive. Sessions are compact, readable, and extremely replayable. It is a small game with enormous mechanical satisfaction.' WHERE title = 'Vampire Survivors';

UPDATE game SET description = 'XCOM 2 is a turn-based tactical strategy game where players lead a resistance movement against alien occupation in a desperate fight for humanity''s future. Missions are tense because every action matters, and the loss of a trained soldier can be emotionally and strategically devastating. The game balances battlefield tactics with wider campaign management, forcing players to split attention between immediate survival and long-term planning. Cover, flanking, abilities, and randomness create dramatic encounters where a perfect plan can still collapse under pressure. Custom soldiers and the memory of past missions help the campaign feel personal. The difficulty can be punishing, but that tension is also what gives victories so much weight. It is one of the strongest modern strategy games for players who enjoy risk, pressure, and consequence.' WHERE title = 'XCOM 2';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Persona 3 Reload is a modern remake of a beloved RPG that combines dungeon crawling, social simulation, and themes of mortality in a stylish package. The game follows a group of students who confront supernatural threats while also navigating school life, friendships, and identity. Its structure creates a compelling contrast between the ordinary routines of daily life and the eerie battles that take place after midnight. Turn-based combat is polished and readable, with elemental weaknesses and party roles giving battles clear strategic shape. The emotional tone is more reflective and somber than in some later Persona entries, which gives the story a distinct weight. Music, interface design, and visual updates help the remake feel fresh without losing the spirit of the original. It is a thoughtful and striking RPG about time, connection, and acceptance.' WHERE title = 'Persona 3 Reload';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Like a Dragon: Infinite Wealth is a large-scale RPG that combines melodrama, humor, turn-based combat, and character warmth in a way few other series attempt. The game continues to build on the strength of its cast, giving major emotional beats room to land while still embracing bizarre side stories and absurd detours. Combat is more playful and spatially expressive than before, making every encounter feel more dynamic. The setting adds variety and helps the adventure feel bigger and more colorful than a typical crime drama. Side activities, minigames, and optional content are extensive, giving the world a sense of excess that fits the series well. Beneath the chaos is a sincere focus on loyalty, aging, regret, and friendship. It is a big-hearted RPG that knows how to balance ridiculous fun with genuine emotion.' WHERE title = 'Like a Dragon: Infinite Wealth';

UPDATE game SET description = 'The Talos Principle 2 is a first-person puzzle game that builds intricate environmental challenges around themes of consciousness, civilization, and philosophical responsibility. Puzzles are carefully layered, often requiring players to understand how multiple systems interact rather than simply spotting one trick. The world is visually beautiful and much larger in scale than many puzzle games, giving the journey a contemplative grandeur. Narrative conversations and written material invite reflection without forcing one rigid interpretation. What makes the game stand out is how successfully it combines mechanical rigor with intellectual curiosity. Progression remains satisfying because every new puzzle still feels grounded in clear rules, even when the ideas become more complex. It is a rare sequel that expands both the brain and the soul of its original.' WHERE title = 'The Talos Principle 2';

UPDATE game SET description = 'RimWorld is a colony simulation and story generator where players manage survivors trying to build a life on a remote world. The game is famous for turning simple systems like mood, health, weather, raids, and relationships into unpredictable narratives full of triumph and disaster. Every colony develops its own identity because characters have distinct traits, weaknesses, and personal histories. Building and resource management are important, but the emotional drama of survival is what makes the game memorable. Crises often emerge from small problems that spiral outward, forcing adaptation instead of routine. The simulation is deep enough to support endless playstyles, from benevolent settlement building to brutal authoritarian control. It is one of the richest sandbox strategy games ever created.' WHERE title = 'RimWorld';

UPDATE game SET description = 'F1 24 is a modern Formula racing game designed around licensed teams, circuit precision, and the tension of high-speed motorsport. Success depends on braking control, corner exits, tire management, and race awareness rather than simple top speed. Career systems and team progression help create a longer arc beyond individual races, giving players reasons to improve and invest over time. Presentation is polished and broadcast-inspired, helping each event feel like part of a larger professional season. Track familiarity and consistent practice are strongly rewarded, which suits the demands of Formula racing. The game works best for players who enjoy measured improvement and technical driving. It is a strong motorsport package built around discipline and speed.' WHERE title = 'F1® 24';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Need for Speed Unbound is a street racing game that mixes arcade driving, city exploration, and a bold visual style built around graffiti-like effects and expressive presentation. The game focuses on illegal racing culture, police pressure, and the constant push to earn more while risking everything. Cars are highly customizable, which helps players feel ownership over both performance and identity. Racing itself is fast and accessible, designed more around style, aggression, and atmosphere than strict realism. The city backdrop supports a sense of rebellious energy, especially during high-risk runs where pursuit and reward escalate together. Its visual direction helps distinguish it from more traditional racers, even when the structure remains familiar. It is a confident arcade racer with attitude and momentum.' WHERE title = 'Need for Speed™ Unbound';

UPDATE game SET description = 'Hunt: Showdown 1896 is a multiplayer extraction shooter that combines gothic horror, tense gunfights, and deliberate pacing in a uniquely oppressive setting. Players enter dangerous maps to track monstrous targets while knowing that rival hunters are doing the same thing. This creates constant tension, because every sound and movement could mean opportunity or sudden death. Weapons feel heavy and old, which slows combat in a way that makes positioning and nerves especially important. The horror atmosphere is not just cosmetic, but central to how the game creates pressure and uncertainty. Matches often produce memorable stories because outcomes can change from one gunshot or one bad decision. It is one of the most distinctive multiplayer shooters for players who enjoy suspense and high stakes.' WHERE title = 'Hunt: Showdown 1896';

COMMIT;